k\": 0.49236915610289683, \"text\": \"Boney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boney_Kapoor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boney_Kapoor\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Abo\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1460}, {\"ngram\": \"the most prestigious universities\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1517}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"mixed emotions\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love coming in here.\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the most fun job in the world.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1616, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most fun job\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1602}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We get to hang out with each other every day, but I am also really excited to see what's out there in the world.\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1729, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oh, my head is spinning right now.\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1764, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1741}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My heart's beating really fast,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1807, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Boney - who is a proud Gamilaroi Gomeroi woman - said she never imagined working on one of Australia's most iconic shows in television.\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1809, \"end\": 1814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boney_Kapoor\", \"score\": 0.5803385184072356, \"rank\": 0.49236915610289683, \"text\": \"Boney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boney_Kapoor\", \"dbpedia\": \